  "body": "### Component\n\nAnvil\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nIt would be nice if it was possible to configure or read the anvil disk cache location via the CLI\r\nhttps://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/blob/c331b5eeee1b4151ef7354a081667e2d770b37f5/anvil/src/config.rs#L1085-L1086 \r\n\r\nUse case: we have a dev script internally running anvil and want to clean the cache before every start. Currently we're hardcoding the location to `~/.foundry/anvil/tmp`, but this is brittle and would break if the cache location is changed upstream.\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
