    "body": "if i kept it running it used up 10Gb in 24 hrs \r\nso i kept having to remember to run the following as i only had about 20Gb free anyway so it was chewing up precious swap disk space, which is especially important on a dual cpu machine with 8gb memory that was always maxed out\r\n```\r\ndu -sh /root/.foundry/anvil/\r\nrm -rf /root/.foundry/anvil/tmp/\r\n```",
